---
import experiences from "../collections/experiences.json";
import AboutExperience from "../components/about-experience.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
import Button from "../components/button.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <section class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-6 z-10">
    <h2
      class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl"
    >
      黄宏昌
    </h2>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-12 items-start justify-start md:flex-row mt-12 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400"
    >
      <div class="w-full md:w-9/12">
        <div
          class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
        >
          Introduce
        </div>
        <div
          class="text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-6"
        >
          目前是一名产品设计师，初级开发者，立志做一名设计工程师。拥有云计算、低代码、电商、智能客服、零信任等多行业洞察与实践落地经验。<br
          /><br />
          我热衷于技术的无限可能性，并开启了简单的编程学习之旅。时至今日，开发了导航工具
          <a href="https://larkmap.com" target="_blank">Larkmap ↗</a
          >（衍生品开源导航工具 <a
            href="https://nav.dippermap.com/"
            target="_blank">Dippermap ↗</a
          >），图标库网站 <a href="https://qingicon.com" target="_blank"
            >QingIcon ↗</a
          > 及配套 Figma 插件 <a
            href="https://www.figma.com/community/plugin/1111565622161029659"
            target="_blank">Figicon ↗</a
          >，B 端产品常见页面布局适配方案 <a
            href="https://adapter.biliui.com"
            target="_blank">Q-Adapter ↗</a
          >，Linear 风格按钮鉴赏 <a
            href="https://btn.biliui.com/"
            target="_blank">Linear Buttons ↗</a
          > 等。<br /><br />
          我专注于探索产品设计的价值观，在极致的设计、交互与技术包容、业务理解之间寻求平衡以解决问题，持续写作与分享，累计输出超
          15 万字的 <a href="https://www.yuque.com/asorn" target="_blank"
            >技术文章 ↗</a
          >。<br /><br />
          除此之外，我曾荣获 3 款外观发明专利，你可以在 <a
            href="http://epub.cnipa.gov.cn/"
            target="_blank">国家知识产权局 ↗</a
          >
          官网中输入我的名字查询。<br /><br />
          如果你有兴趣，还可以来 <a
            href="https://www.yuque.com/asorn"
            target="_blank">语雀 ↗</a
          >
          看看我种草的影视剧作品，偶尔写的中二文章，日常收集的奇思妙想。<br
          /><br />
          如果你也玩小红书，看看我发布的 <a
            href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/user/profile/58febdab50c4b4527ef0dc09"
            target="_blank">生活笔记 ↗</a
          >，说不定，我们能找到共鸣。
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full mt-10 md:w-3/12 md:mt-0">
        <div>
          <div
            class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
          >
            Contact
          </div>
          <span class="block text-sm mb-1"
            >邮箱：<a href="mailto:1208774030@qq.com">1208774030@qq.com</a
            ></span
          >
          <span class="block text-sm"
            >手机：<a href="tel:你的手机号">你的手机号</a></span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <div
            class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
          >
            Resume
          </div>
          <span class="block text-xs text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-500"
            >下载我的简历 (PDF & 1MB)</span
          >
          <Button text="下载简历" link="" />
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <div
            class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
          >
            Portfolio
          </div>
          <span class="block text-xs text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-500"
            >下载我的作品集 (PDF & 8MB)</span
          >
          <Button
            text="下载作品集"
            link="https://astro.s3.bitiful.net/blog/about/黄宏昌- UI设计师2023.pdf"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <img
      src="https://astro.s3.bitiful.net/blog/about/about.jpg"
      class="relative z-30 w-full my-10 rounded-xl"
    />
    <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200">Short Bio</h2>
    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg"
    >
      Front-end cutter 🧑🏻‍💻, back-end amateur 🤷🏻‍♂️, operations digging holes person
      🤦🏻‍♂️.
    </p>

    <h2
      class="mt-5 mb-2 text-2xl font-bold lg:mt-10 sm:mt-6 dark:text-neutral-200"
    >
      Experience
    </h2>
    <div class="group/list pl-5 py-10">
      {
        experiences.map((experience, index) => {
          const isLastItem = index === experiences.length - 1;
          return (
            <>
              <div
                class={`pb-10 ${isLastItem ? "" : "border-l border-gray-200 dark:border-neutral-700"}`}
              >
                <AboutExperience
                  dates={experience.dates}
                  role={experience.role}
                  company={experience.company}
                  description={experience.description}
                  logo={experience.logo}
                />
              </div>
            </>
          );
        })
      }
    </div>

    <h2
      class="text-2xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-200"
    >
      Let's Connect
    </h2>
    <p
      class="text-sm leading-6 lg:mb-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400 sm:leading-7 lg:leading-8 sm:text-base lg:text-lg sm:mb-40"
    >
      If you want to stay up to date with my work be sure to <a
        href="https://twitter.com/ccikai"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-indigo-600 underline">follow me on twitter</a
      >, or you can send me an <a
        href="mailto:astro-aria@miantiao.me"
        class="text-indigo-600 underline">email</a
      > and I'll be sure to get back to you.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>